Having a small kitchen comes with several challenges, the most obvious being that you’re extremely limited on counter space. Because of this, getting creative with where you put things and being thoughtful about what kind of gadgets and tools you buy in the first place are always priorities when you’re on the hunt for new goodies. But luckily for you, many brands understand this struggle and have created small-space-friendly appliances that don’t require you to sacrifice quality. From a compact air fryer to a mini Nespresso machine to a tiny rice cooker, below we listed 11 must-have appliances that you and your lack of counter space will thank you for. And they’re all easily purchasable on Amazon. HuffPost may receive a share from purchases made via links on this page. Every item is independently selected by the HuffPost Shopping team. Prices and availability are subject to change.